summary: free-form tags for easy filtering

decription:
    Throughout the years, free-form tags proved to be useful for many,
    many scenarios. Primarily to provide an easy way how to select a
    subset of objects.

story:
    - As a developer/tester I would like to run only a subset of
      available tests.

examples: |
    tags: [Tier1, fast]

notes:
    Tags are case-sensitive.
    Using lowercase is recommended.

type: list
